{"tid":1569100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反分化，聚力量","createTime":"2019-09-14T13:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T13:49:51.000Z","uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1135b40362dc7392da72e322b564145a2522fa22","tid":1569100,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:17:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n長話短說<br />\n<br />\n1.唱願榮光同今天我係兩回事，願榮光係大家親身經歷既故事，係用戰友既血交織出黎既故事，黑警每打一棍，首歌就越有感染力，唔好再用今天我呢d抒情歌比。<br />\n<br />\n2.一區有難，十七區支援，唔好再講送唔送頭，呢場係一場漫長既戰役，人心士氣係致勝關鍵，你今日伸唔入黎幫我，下次你區有事點解要幫你?憑咩要幫你?外區支援唔洗勇武唔洗出手，你人到口到就已經夠振奮人心。請下次大叫&times;&times;區黎支援&times;&times;區，18區打倒黑社會。係媒體前攞左分先。<br />\n<br />\n3.唔好理有無左膠擋，下次確定係落單藍絲，抽左水先，一人抽一下佢都死，筆啊針啊筷子咩都好，拮左先，春袋同腰，快拮快閃下一個再拮。<br />\n<br />\n再有指責post唔該全腐皮，人多就係我地既力量，你敢出我地就多一分勝算，唔通佢拉得晒200萬人。</span>"},{"pid":"ad2a7a568c2e0fcf0bcbc4b6abe8d082c0b2065a","tid":1569100,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9ae41e282cd63bae32fb07f27e0ed4fc3f562c8","tid":1569100,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:42:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70771ecb7473a2408d6644f09a85f16d12c55755","tid":1569100,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82c70d19dfc63494218b0b31c077e0d0ca8fdc1d","tid":1569100,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}